{"title":"给播种者","authors":["于永田"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":1,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给播种者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于永田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来不及把丰收的喜悦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏进心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又引犁深耕了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这片黑色的土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要把心和种子一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播进这肥沃的土里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让嫩绿的幼苗笑迎冬季。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望降下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几场鹅毛大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让她们经受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪的洗礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多一场飞雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就多一份丰收的希冀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你懂得："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不是百分之百的温暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与冰拥抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶凌吐绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼苗才不会贻害自己！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝视着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散发芳香的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子还未播下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，你的眼前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是铺天盖地的飞雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正化做万顷麦浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌向天际……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}